TY  - JOUR
TI  - Computing Simply Stable Equilibria
AU  - Wilson, Robert
AB  - [For each two-player game, a linear-programming algorithm finds a component of the Nash equilibria and a subset of its perfect equilibria that are simply stable: there are nearby equilibria for each nearby game that perturbs one strategy's probability or payoff more than others.]
